[Verse 1: L.I.F.E. Long]
Fresh out the Hudson, it’s the Queens and Bronx brethren
Residing out in Brooknam, we got cousins out in Shaolin
In a circle from Strong Island, Decepticons combining
Lo-Lives up in the Polo Mansion wiling, Gazelles and
Kangols [?] styling.  Feel the strength
Of the city.  Ayyo, we’re more than just an island

[Verse 2: C-Rayz Walz]
(C-Rayz) True to class (BX) ‘cause the truth is multiplying
Do the math on the path in blood diamonds, turn-
Turnstyles (Trash), Chuck-Chuckers, bubblegoose
Loosies, crackheads, boxcutters, hustle-proof
[?] spot hot, poppy got butter
Pot brothers with baby mothers
Brothers snitching, (Muah) Kiss my ass
Jada still spit heroine lines
Sniff N.Y.C. veteran rhymes
Stronghold sign up in the sky, see?

